---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Makeaway</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A personal field guide for building a freer life through hiking, side projects, money, travel, and figuring things out along the way."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <img
        class="site-logo"
        src="/makeaway-logo-transparent.png"
        alt="Make a Way logo"
      />

      <h1>A personal field guide for building a freer life.</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Notes on hiking, escaping the rat race, side projects, money, travel,
        and figuring things out along the way.
      </p>

      <section class="cards">
        <a class="card" href="/escape">
          <h2>Escape</h2>
          <p>
            Thoughts on work, burnout, freedom, and designing a life that feels
            more your own.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/outside">
          <h2>Outside</h2>
          <p>
            Hiking, camping, nature, gear, and the places that reset your brain.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/build">
          <h2>Build</h2>
          <p>
            Side projects, websites, experiments, and learning new skills by
            actually making things.
          </p>
          <a class="card" href="/game">
           <h2>Game</h2>
           <p>
                Play Trail Runner — a small Makeaway jumping game for desktop and phone.
           </p>
          </a>
        </a>

        <a class="card" href="/money">
          <h2>Money</h2>
          <p>
            Investing, dividends, options, and the long road toward more
            independence.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/articles">
          <h2>Articles</h2>
          <p>
            Investing, dividends, options, and the long road toward more
            independence.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/land">
  <h2>Land</h2>
  <p>
    Research notes for the Camden County land, A-F zoning, family compound
    possibilities, and homestead due diligence.
  </p>
  <a class="card" href="/education">
  <h2>Education</h2>
  <p>
    Useful learning resources, tools, guides, and websites for building a freer,
    more capable life.
  </p>
</a>
<a class="card" href="/recipes">
  <h2>Recipes</h2>
  <p>
    Simple meals, camp cooking, homestead recipes, and practical food ideas for
    building a more self-sufficient life.
  </p>
</a>
</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    color: #f5f1e8;
    background: #172117;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124, 185, 9, 0.25), transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #111811, #0c2002);
  }

  main {
    width: min(980px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 96px 0;
  }

  .site-logo {
    width: min(520px, 100%);
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 34px;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: #ded8c8;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

   .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(210px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 72px;
  }

  .card,
  .card:visited {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.18);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition:
      transform 180ms ease,
      border-color 180ms ease,
      background 180ms ease,
      box-shadow 180ms ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(201, 216, 166, 0.7);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  }

  .card:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid #c9d8a6;
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }

  .card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #f5f1e8;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #d5ccb8;
    line-height: 1.55;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    main {
      padding: 64px 0;
    }

    .site-logo {
      width: min(420px, 100%);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>